      • planMutationsForSet

        List<scala.Tuple2<MutationType,Dataset<Row>>> planMutationsForSet(Dataset<Row> arriving)
        Plan the bulk mutations for the arriving DataFrame from the step.
        Parameters:
        arriving - The DataFrame from the step.
        Returns:
        A list of bulk mutations, where each mutation is composed of a tuple of a mutation type and a mutation DataFrame. The mutations will be applied in the same order as the list.
